title: Malicious Chrome Extension Grants Full Control Over Ethereum Wallet

content.raw: Security researchers have uncovered a sophisticated supply chain attack disguised as a legitimate cryptocurrency wallet. Socket’s Threat Research Team discovered a malicious Chrome extension called “Safery: Ethereum Wallet,” published on the Chrome Web Store on November 12, 2024, that employs an ingenious technique to steal user seed phrases through hidden blockchain transactions.
